summary: Some more Beetlejuice the musical pen drawings. I swear I have drawn Beej and Adam the most since I’m seen the musical. I need...
body: Some more Beetlejuice the musical pen drawings. I swear I have drawn Beej and Adam the most since I’m seen the musical. I need to draw more of the rest of the cast. I loved Beetlejuice’s wedding outfit and I was in a mad rush to draw what I could remember about it. I can’t wait to see it again…at least can I get a soundtrack to hold me over.

summary: Happy 30th anniversary to Sandman! Several years ago my now fiance told me to read her favorite comic of all time, Sandman by...
caption: Happy 30th anniversary to Sandman! Several years ago my now fiance told me to read her favorite comic of all time, Sandman by @neilhimself. It has truly helped me visualize stories and we’ve adopted the tradition of reading this masterpiece every year during Xmas. A gift that keeps on giving.
